name: Helpdesk
query:
select
`tabRequest`.name as "Request Id:Link/Request:200",
`tabRequest`.requester_name as "Requester:Data:100",
`tabRequest`.requester_email_id as "Requester Email Id:Data:170",
`tabRequest`.sub_request_category as "Sub Request Category:Data:150",
`tabRequest`.request_category as "Request Category:Data:150",
`tabRequest`.subject as "Subject:Data:150",
`tabRequest`.priority as "Priority:Data:80",
`tabRequest`.current_status as "Current Status:Data:200",
`tabRequest`.request_status as "Status:Data:80"
from 
`tabRequest`
